OL,3,C'Release the tapes': Bath MP Wera
OL,4,CHobhouse refutes Hong Kong claims
OL,6,FA West Country MP who was denied entry
OL,7,Finto Hong Kong wants the recording of
OL,8,Fher deportation to be released
OL,9,Fpublicly as diplomatic tensions
OL,10,Fcontinue to rise.
OL,12,FWera Hobhouse, the Liberal Democrat MP
OL,13,Ffor Bath, was turned away by
OL,14,Fimmigration officials after flying to
OL,15,FHong Kong to visit her son and newborn
OL,16,Fgrandson last week.
