OL,3,C'Release the tapes': Bath MP Wera
OL,4,CHobhouse refutes Hong Kong claims
OL,6,FFollowing an appeal by Foreign
OL,7,FSecretary David Lammy, Chinese
OL,8,Fauthorities issued a statement
OL,9,Fimplying Ms Hobhouse did not comply
OL,10,Fwith officials.
OL,12,FBut Ms Hobhouse, who denies the
OL,13,Fclaims, insists she answered "every
OL,14,Fquestion asked of me".
OL,16,F'Release the tapes' - Bath MP
OL,18,F"This attempt by the authorities to
OL,19,Fsmear me and cast doubt on my account
OL,20,Fis hugely upsetting but sadly not
OL,21,Fsurprising," she said.
