OL,3,C'Release the tapes': Bath MP Wera
OL,4,CHobhouse refutes Hong Kong claims
OL,6,F"I was polite and cooperative
OL,7,Fthroughout the interview, answering
OL,8,Fevery question asked of me.
OL,10,F"I even volunteered personal
OL,11,Finformation I wasn't asked for, such
OL,12,Fas showing officials a picture of my
OL,13,Fbaby grandson who was waiting for me
OL,14,Fon the other side.
OL,16,F"If the Chinese or Hong Kong SAR
OL,17,Fauthorities want to assert that I did
OL,18,Fnot answer questions from immigration
OL,19,Fofficials, they have to provide some
OL,20,Fevidence.
