OL,3,C'Release the tapes': Bath MP Wera
OL,4,CHobhouse refutes Hong Kong claims
OL,6,F"Surely they have a tape, or a
OL,7,Ftranscript of the interview. Release
OL,8,Fthe tapes and let me know what I did
OL,9,Fnot answer."
OL,11,FMs Hobhouse, one of more than 40
OL,12,Fparliamentarians of the Inter-
OL,13,FParliamentary Alliance on China (Ipac)
OL,14,Fwhich is critical of Beijing's record
OL,15,Fon human rights, is believed to be the
OL,16,Ffirst MP to be refused entry to the
OL,17,Fformer British colony since it was
OL,18,Fhanded back to China in 1997.
