OL,3,C'Release the tapes': Bath MP Wera
OL,4,CHobhouse refutes Hong Kong claims
OL,6,FIn their statement, a Hong Kong
OL,7,Fgovernment spokesperson said it was
OL,8,F"the duty of (an) immigration officer
OL,9,Fto ask questions to ascertain that
OL,10,Fthere is no doubt about the purpose of
OL,11,Fany visit.
OL,13,F"The person concerned knows best what
OL,14,Fhe or she has done. It will be
OL,15,Funhelpful to the person's case if the
OL,16,Fperson refuses to answer questions put
OL,17,Fto him or her for that purpose."
